/* 
  Localizable.strings (English)
  SwiftAI Boilerplate Pro
  
  English (Base) translations
  
  ## How to Add New Strings:
  1. Add the key here following the pattern: "namespace.key" = "Value";
  2. Add corresponding property in L10n.swift
  3. Copy this file to other language folders and translate
  
  ## Key Naming Convention:
  - Use lowercase with dots: auth.signIn.apple
  - Group by feature: auth.*, chat.*, settings.*
  - Use camelCase after dot: auth.signInApple (NOT auth.sign_in_apple)
*/

